1. *Gospodina* je pogledala u njegove oči i osmehnula se. (She looked into his eyes and smiled.)

2. *Gospodinu* su se obratili sa pitanjima. (They addressed him with questions.)

3. *Gospodina* je pozdravio njegov najbolji prijatelj. (His best friend greeted him.)

4. Ona je otišla za *gospodinom* u njegovu kancelariju. (She went to his office with him.)

5. *Gospodina* je zaustavila policija. (The police stopped him.)

6. Ona je pronašla *gospodina* u parku. (She found him in the park.)

7. *Gospodinu* su pronašli izgubljenu mačku. (They found his lost cat.)

8. *Gospodina* su pozvali da govori na skupu. (They invited him to speak at the gathering.)